    <string name="user_interface_accessibility_settings_title">Shut off screen</string>
    <string name="user_interface_accessibility_settings_summary">
        When the screen is locked, long tap to shut off the screen again.
        Use the system\'s accessibility settings to enable the downloaded app Öffi.
    </string>
    <string name="user_interface_accessibility_service_description">
        When in navigation mode and the device wakes up without becoming unlocked,
        you can switch off the screen by long tapping on the screen.
        The app does not read your screen or interact in any other way with the device.
    </string>

